[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/5601][img]https://github.com/rdok/7daystodie_mod_immersive_crosshair/blob/main/documentation/showcase.gif?raw=true[/img][/url]

[size=5]Features[/size]
[list]
[*] Shows crosshair only when holding a tool/hands and hovering crosshair close to any interactable object.
[*] Shows crosshair having the interaction prompted opened (interact with cars/doors/etc...), regardless of equipped tool or weapon.
[*] Gears mod settings integration supported. In game options to optionally enable crosshair when:
[list]
[*] wielding any bow with no sights.   
[*] wielding any tool or using hands only.
[*] wielding any melee weapon.
[*] Requires [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/4017]Gears[/url] &  [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/2409/]Quartz[/url]
[*] For an example visit the [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/5601?tab=videos#lg=2&slide=0]Videos tab[/url].[/list]
[*] This mod has been designed to optionally work with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/5640]Dot Crosshair[/url]
[*] Game Version: 1.0. Install with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/about/vortex/]Vortex[/url].
[/list]
